claude-code-usage-monitor for Debian
====================================

This package installs the `claude-monitor` CLI (plus aliases from upstream)
for monitoring Claude Code usage in a terminal UI.

Upstream project:
    https://github.com/Maciek-roboblog/Claude-Code-Usage-Monitor

Debian-specific notes:
    - Configuration and runtime behavior follow upstream defaults.
    - No Debian-specific patches are applied at this time.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Mon, 13 Apr 2026 17:15:00 +0200
